---
title: Roast Root Veggie & Crouton Salad with Creamy Pesto, Toasted Pecans & Feta
description: The best salads are a combination of flavours, textures and colours – and with golden roasted kumara, herby wholemeal croutons, earthy beetroot and creamy feta, this salad ticks all the boxes.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

